{
  "texts": [
    "To remove potential model indicators from responses, they were transformed into plain text before being distributed to three clinicians and three diabetes patients.",
    "They all analyzed responses across six rounds spaced 48 hours apart to eliminate confounding.",
    "(Figure 2) Responses for each model and raw scores for evaluation are provided in Appendix 3.",
    "Accuracy evaluationWe conducted an accuracy evaluation for each response by assigning scores and ratings.",
    "A \"Poor\" rating received 1 point, \"Borderline\" received 2 points, and \"Good\" received 3 points."
  ]
}